<C>__{roberta}
<D>__{ok...}
<P>__{(not believing it)}
<D>__{it's gonna be o.k.}
<A>__{she crosses to take a look at her music, and the kids exchange looks that say, "oh shit. what did we just promise?" rehearsal montage series of shots day}
